除此之外，其他内容和 LEVEL1 都相同，那我们用相同的脚本，password 改一下，然后去读取日志即可：

#### EXP
```c
#include<stdio.h>
#include<stdlib.h>
#include<fcntl.h>
#include<unistd.h>
#include<string.h>

#define PATH "/proc/pwncollege"

int main(){
    int fd;
    char *password = "seywmafciuspxdbdf";
    ssize_t written;

    fd = open(PATH,O_WRONLY);
    written = write(fd, password, strlen(password));
    printf("write successfully!\n");
    close(fd);

    return EXIT_SUCCESS;

} 

```

运行 exp 之后查看日志，得到flag：`dmesg | tail -n 20`

