着重强调一下 read1 函数：

```c
unsigned __int64 __fastcall read_1(__int64 a1, size_t size)
{
  unsigned __int64 size_2; // rax
  int v3; // [rsp+1Ch] [rbp-14h]
  unsigned __int64 size_1; // [rsp+20h] [rbp-10h]

  for ( size_1 = 0; ; size_1 += v3 )
